| 200,000 &lt;small&gt;(up to 1992)&lt;/small&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;small&gt;(''[[Street Fighter II: The World Warrior|The World Warrior]]'': 60,000 &lt;br&gt; ''[[Street Fighter II′: Champion Edition|Champion Edition]]'': 140,000)&lt;/small&gt;{{refn|''Street Fighter II'':
