{{short description|17th-century German scientist, inventor, and politician}}
{{Infobox scientist
|name              = Otto von Guericke
|image             = Anselmus-van-Hulle-Hommes-illustres_MG_0539.tif
|image_size        =
|caption           = Otto von Guericke, engraving after a portrait by [[Anselm van Hulle]] (1601–1674)
|birth_name        = Otto Gericke
|birth_date        = {{birth-date|November 30, 1602}}
